+**Locations:** `mobile/src/theme/colors.ts` (`colors.tier`), `web/positional-tiers.html` (inline CSS: `.tier-row`, `.tier-assign-btn`, `.tier-legend-swatch`), `web/profile.html` (inline CSS vars `--elite`…`--bench`), `extension/content.css` (`.ftf-badge.ftf-tier-*`).
