+
+**Known collision:** Depth purple `#a855f7` is also the TE position color (`--te` in web CSS, `te` in `mobile/src/theme/colors.ts`). The previous Depth orange collided with QB the same way. If either the Depth tier or TE position color changes, a human should decide the pairing deliberately.
 
